snippet.title: CryoFall - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
CryoFall - the multiplayer survival RPG brought to you by AtomicTorch Studio and Daedalic Entertainment - OUT NOW on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/829590/CryoFall/

-- About the Game --
CryoFall is a Sci-Fi multiplayer survival game set on a forgotten planet in a distant future. Master technology, trading, crafting, industry, farming, exploration and more! 

-- Developed by AtomicTorch Studio --
http://atomictorch.com/

-- Follow us on Social Media -- 
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/daedalic 
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/daedalic 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/daedalicentertainment

https://www.daedalic.com
